%% Trainer Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-3.4-ea.1/trainer.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Trainer Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as Trainer Controller<br/>controller-runtime
    participant Worker as Training Pod (Primary Worker)<br/>28080/TCP HTTP
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>OpenShift Monitoring

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 1: TrainJob Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: POST TrainJob CR<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate TrainJob<br/>HTTPS/9443, API server client cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response (allow/deny)
    K8sAPI-->>User: TrainJob created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch TrainJob events<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: TrainJob event notification

    Controller->>K8sAPI: GET TrainingRuntime/ClusterTrainingRuntime<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Runtime spec

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Apply JobSet (server-side apply)<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update TrainJob status<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 2: Progression Tracking (RHAI)

    loop Every 30s (configurable 5s-300s)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: List pods (find primary worker rank 0)<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Pod list with IPs
        Controller->>Worker: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/28080, plaintext<br/>NetworkPolicy-restricted
        Worker-->>Controller: JSON: progress %, steps, epochs, ETA
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Patch TrainJob annotations<br/>trainer.opendatahub.io/trainerStatus
    end

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 3: Prometheus Metrics Scraping

    Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>HTTPS/8443, TLS<br/>insecureSkipVerify: true
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics
